So Crux is this old man!

270
00:16:54,410 --> 00:16:56,760
Yes! His nickname is Crumudgeon!

271
00:16:58,150 --> 00:17:00,460
It's kind of sudden, but I have a request.

272
00:17:00,460 --> 00:17:05,150
Can you use your power to look into the Celestial 
Wizard that Loke was with in the past, Crumudgeon?

273
00:17:16,710 --> 00:17:18,730
He's asleep, Lucy!

274
00:17:18,730 --> 00:17:20,940
Don't worry, he's looking things up.

275
00:17:20,940 --> 00:17:23,640
You're lying! He's totally asleep!

276
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:26,940
Crumudgeon is a specialist in Celestial Studies.

277
00:17:26,940 --> 00:17:31,340
He knows everything about the gates that 
connect the Spirit World with the human one.

278
00:17:31,340 --> 00:17:36,260
He knows all about what Celestial Wizards 
could call out which spirits in the past.

279
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:40,820
Did you find something?

280
00:17:41,850 --> 00:17:48,940
I cannot be too detailed as personal information
is protected even in the spirit world, however,

281
00:17:48,940 --> 00:17:54,840
the Celestial Wizard connected 
to Loke is Karen Lilica.

282
00:17:55,840 --> 00:17:57,470
Karen Lilica?

283
00:17:58,010 --> 00:18:00,280
You know her, Lucy?

284
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:03,090
She's a super-famous Celestial Wizard.

285
00:18:03,090 --> 00:18:07,540
Extremely beautiful, and she used 
to do photo shoots for Sorcerer.

286
00:18:07,540 --> 00:18:11,630
But some years ago she died while on a job.

287
00:18:11,630 --> 00:18:13,790
So she was a guild wizard.

288
00:18:13,790 --> 00:18:17,190
Yeah. Blue Pegasus, if I recall.

289
00:18:18,810 --> 00:18:22,720
So... What was the relationship 
between Loke and Karen?

290
00:18:23,600 --> 00:18:26,410
I am sorry, but that is all I can say.

291
00:18:26,620 --> 00:18:27,700
Hey!

292
00:18:30,700 --> 00:18:33,390
He's researching again!

293
00:18:33,390 --> 00:18:35,270
No, he's asleep.

294
00:18:37,010 --> 00:18:38,600
Karen and Loke...

295
00:18:39,490 --> 00:18:42,540
I don't have long to live.

296
00:18:42,540 --> 00:18:43,300
Wait...

297
00:18:44,150 --> 00:18:48,670
Do you understand the sorrow of a star 
that cannot return to the heavens?

298
00:18:49,180 --> 00:18:51,900
He can't mean... Loke?

299
00:18:51,900 --> 00:18:53,520
What's the matter, Lucy?

300
00:18:55,280 --> 00:18:57,030
Lucy, we have a problem!

301
00:18:57,650 --> 00:19:00,530
Loke's gone and left Fairy Tail!

302
00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:02,900
W-Why?

303
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:06,090
We don't know! Everyone's searching for him.

304
00:19:06,090 --> 00:19:09,180
He's been acting totally weird lately.

305
00:19:09,620 --> 00:19:10,500
It couldn't be...

306
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:13,150
Hey, Lucy!

307
00:19:13,150 --> 00:19:14,980
Where are you going to look for him?

308
00:19:15,460 --> 00:19:17,400
Loke!

309
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:19,300
Where are you?

310
00:19:19,550 --> 00:19:20,700
Loke!

311
00:19:20,700 --> 00:19:21,840
Loke!

312
00:19:22,420 --> 00:19:23,680
You in there, Loke?

313
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:25,010
I doubt it.

314
00:19:25,290 --> 00:19:26,830
Loke!

315
00:19:26,830 --> 00:19:28,190
Loke!

316
00:19:55,580 --> 00:19:56,630
Loke!

317
00:19:58,230 --> 00:19:59,230
Lucy.

318
00:19:59,690 --> 00:20:01,390
Everyone's searching for you.

319
00:20:03,150 --> 00:20:05,590
That's Karen's grave, isn't it?

320
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:11,170
The Celestial Wizard Karen... Your owner.

321
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:15,000
Spirit Loke...

322
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:18,300
No... Your real name is...

323
00:20:21,170 --> 00:20:23,330
Leo, the Lion!

324
00:20:34,260 --> 00:20:38,190
You did well to realize I was actually a spirit.

325
00:20:38,190 --> 00:20:43,110
Well, I am a Celestial Wizard 
with contracts with many spirits.

326
00:20:43,110 --> 00:20:45,560
I finally figured out the truth behind you.

327
00:20:46,220 --> 00:20:49,680
But I should have noticed 
it sooner, shouldn't I?

328
00:20:50,410 --> 00:20:56,040
After an incident where the owner dies, 
their contract with the spirit is nullified.

329
00:20:56,040 --> 00:21:01,150
Then the spirit is forced back to the 
spirit world until a new owner appears.

330
00:21:01,940 --> 00:21:07,390
Karen died, so the contract should be over, 
and yet you're here in the human world.

331
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:12,070
For some reason, you can't return 
to the spirit world, can you?

332
00:21:13,810 --> 00:21:19,440
Just as humans can't live in the spirit world, 
spirits can't live forever in the human world.

333
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:21,810
Your spirit life-energy will 
be slowly drained from you,

334
00:21:21,810 --> 00:21:23,830
and finally you will meet your end.

335
00:21:24,140 --> 00:21:26,470
It's already been 3 years.

336
00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:30,780
T-Three years? I couldn't fathom even one!

337
00:21:31,870 --> 00:21:33,580
I'm at my limit...

338
00:21:33,580 --> 00:21:35,560
I don't have any strength left at all.

339
00:21:35,810 --> 00:21:38,990
I might be able to save you somehow!

340
00:21:38,990 --> 00:21:43,380
Tell me why you can't return! 
I'll open the gate for you!

341
00:21:44,100 --> 00:21:45,940
I don't need to be saved.

342
00:21:45,940 --> 00:21:47,350
What are you saying?

343
00:21:47,350 --> 00:21:50,280
At this rate you're really going to die!

344
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:52,740
The reason I can't go back is simple.

345
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:58,160
I broke a fundamental rule 
between owner and spirit.

346
00:21:58,160 --> 00:22:03,160
And because of it, I have been banished 
from the spirit world for all eternity.

347
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:05,910
Banished... for eternity?

348
00:22:05,910 --> 00:22:08,220
It is my crime.

349
00:22:08,220 --> 00:22:10,680
I shall accept even death.

350
00:22:12,340 --> 00:22:14,650
As a spirit, I am a traitor.

351
00:22:14,900 --> 00:22:16,920
My owner was Karen...

352
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:18,780
And with my own hands...

353
00:22:19,310 --> 00:22:20,490
...I killed her.

354
00:23:56,330 --> 00:23:59,360
I wonder what the spirit world is like?

355
00:23:59,360 --> 00:24:03,750
Natsu, you went through the spirit world 
once while grabbing onto Virgo, right?

356
00:24:03,750 --> 00:24:05,540
Didn't you see back then?

357
00:24:05,540 --> 00:24:09,000
It was all so sudden. I was 
gone before I even realized it.

358
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:11,300
Oh! I might have gotten a 
glimpse of something, though...

359
00:24:11,300 --> 00:24:12,940
Ooh, what?

360
00:24:12,940 --> 00:24:13,550
Mustache?

361
00:24:14,140 --> 00:24:16,550
Next time: The Spirit King!

362
00:24:16,550 --> 00:24:18,930
Mustache? What's that supposed to mean?

363
00:24:18,930 --> 00:24:21,640
You'll just have to tune 
in next time to find out!

364
00:24:21,880 --> 00:24:23,770
Now that's a classic preview line!

365
00:24:23,990 --> 00:24:26,240


